::  layer 5: under construction (axes may change)
~%  %four  +  ~
|%
::  bitwise xor
++  mix                                                 ::  binary xor
  ~/  %mix
  |=  [a=@ b=@]
  ^-  @
  =+  [c=0 d=0]
  |-
  ?:  ?&(=(0 a) =(0 b))  d
  %=  $
    a   (~(rsh block 0) 1 a)
    b   (~(rsh block 0) 1 b)
    c   +(c)
    d   (add d (~(lsh block 0) c =((~(end block 0) 1 a) (~(end block 0) 1 b))))
  ==
++  pair
